reviewText: I cannot give this 5 stars due to the cost.  I love the concept, love the labels, love the receipts, but would never pay more than $5 for them.  Maybe I'm cheap . . . who am I kidding?  I am cheap.  I like to save money.  For me, I cannot justify the expense of this luxury.  Other than the price, the product is wonderful - I dare say PERFECT!
